snippet.title: Wo Long: Fallen Dynasty - DLC 2 | Conqueror of Jiangdong Trailer
snippet.description:
The second DLC, "Conqueror of Jiangdong", will be available on September 27.

Take on the demon-plagued Three Kingdoms and overcome the odds of deadly combat!
